Class Empire

  • java.lang.Object
    • kingdoms.kingdoms.Province
      • kingdoms.kingdoms.Duchy
        • kingdoms.kingdoms.Kingdom
          • kingdoms.kingdoms.Empire
  • public class Empire
extends Kingdom

    Implements an empire - a higher level of state that holds at least one kingdom. It has all parametres of a kingdom and additionaly a influence level
